---
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about__inner">
    <div class="about__left">
      <span class="about__eyebrow">About Us</span>
      <h2 class="about__title">Built to Transform<br/>Cross-Border Sourcing</h2>
      <p class="about__intro">
        China remains the world's manufacturing powerhouse and one of the most
        strategic supply markets for businesses seeking scale, variety, and cost
        advantage. One Gate is a B2B sourcing and procurement gateway that helps
        businesses access this market with stronger control, greater efficiency,
        and higher commercial readiness.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about__right">
      <div class="about__block">
        <div class="about__block-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="9.5" stroke="#18442A" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <path d="M11 2c0 0-4 3-4 9s4 9 4 9M11 2c0 0 4 3 4 9s-4 9-4 9M2 11h18" stroke="#18442A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="about__block-title">Direct Supply Access</h3>
          <p class="about__block-text">
            Reach broader supply networks with fewer unnecessary layers.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about__block">
        <div class="about__block-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
            <path d="M4 11h14M4 6h14M4 16h8" stroke="#18442A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <circle cx="17" cy="16" r="3.5" stroke="#18442A" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="about__block-title">Built for Growth</h3>
          <p class="about__block-text">
            Source with a model designed for scale, speed, and better decision-making.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 9rem 2.5rem;
    background: white;
  }

  .about__inner {
    max-width: 1160px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about__eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--forest);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about__title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #0c1c12;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .about__intro {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.82;
    color: #5c6660;
  }

  /* Value blocks */
  .about__right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }

  .about__block {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--off-white);
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(24, 68, 42, 0.06);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .about__block:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(24, 68, 42, 0.08);
  }

  .about__block-icon {
    width: 46px;
    height: 46px;
    background: rgba(24, 68, 42, 0.09);
    border-radius: 13px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .about__block-title {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0c1c12;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about__block-text {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.68;
    color: #6a7870;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3.5rem;
    }

    .about__right {
      padding-top: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
